DESCRIPTION
-----------

C.A.C (Calculator, Algebra, Calculus) is an interactive mathematics learning
platform developed by FruitySoup Studio. The application provides AI-assisted
mathematical education covering arithmetic, algebra, and calculus concepts
through an intuitive web-based interface.

